{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/center-text-with-bootstrap","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Centriranje teksta pomoću Bootstrappa","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada koristimo Bootstrap, možemo centrirati naš element naslova sekcije kako bi izgledao bolje. Sve što je potrebno jeste dodavanje klase <code>text-center</code> na naš element <code>h2</code>.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da možete dodati više klasa na jedan element razdvajanjem prostora, kao ovde:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;h2 class=\"red-text text-center\">your text&#x3C;/h2>\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd8acde08812","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16771,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/center-text-with-bootstrap"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\r\n<style>\r\n  .red-text {\r\n    color: red;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: Lobster, Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  p {\r\n    font-size: 16px;\r\n    font-family: Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .thick-green-border {\r\n    border-color: green;\r\n    border-width: 10px;\r\n    border-style: solid;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .smaller-image {\r\n    width: 100px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"red-text\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\r\n\r\n  <p>Click here for <a href=\"#\">cat photos</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n  <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"smaller-image thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\r\n\r\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Tuxedo cats running on dirt ground.\">\r\n  <p>Things cats love:</p>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>catnip</li>\r\n    <li>laser pointers</li>\r\n    <li>lasagna</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li>flea treatment</li>\r\n    <li>thunder</li>\r\n    <li>other cats</li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Indoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Loving</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Crazy</label>\r\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\r\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\r\n  </form>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>h2</code> treba da bude centriran koristeći klasu <code>text-center</code></p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('h2')?.classList?.contains('text-center'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>h2</code> takođe mora imati klasu <code>red-text</code></p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('h2')?.classList?.contains('red-text'));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#bootstrap","dashedName":"center-text-with-bootstrap","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-